Basemap:
https://matplotlib.org/basemap/users/installing.html

Download tar.gz file to /miniconda3/pkgs
Untar the file: gunzip -c FILENAME.tar.gz | tar xopf -
cd into the basemaps folder

for GEOS: 
>>> cd geos-3.3.3
>>> export GEOS_DIR=/miniconda3/pkgs/
>>> ./configure --prefix=$GEOS_DIR
>>> make; make install
